>\u00a0series; and there <em>has<\/em>\u00a0been progress on the next arc, it&#8217;s just slow progress. \u00a0This is still going faster than &#8220;real&#8221; books usually come out.<\/p>\n<p>Much thanks go to all the contributors of the <a href=\"http:\/\/www.reddit.com\/r\/HPMOR\/comments\/ueduz\/authors_britpick_thread_ch_137\/\">HPMOR Ch. 1-37 Britpick Thread<\/a> on the r\/HPMOR subreddit, with special gratitude to <strong>noking<\/strong>\u00a0for compiling all the suggestions into a single page &#8211; this was tremendously helpful in executing the changes.<\/p>\n<p>Next Progress Update on August 1st, 2012 at 10pm Pacific Time.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>(This was supposed to post automatically. \u00a0It did not. \u00a0I apologize for that.) Real life still slaying me. \u00a0I did manage to put out the new, British English versions of Ch. 1-17, with significant tweaks to the writing in Ch. &hellip; <a href=\"https:\/\/hpmor.com\/notes\/progress-12-07-01\/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&rarr;<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_mi_skip_tracking":false,"_s2mail":"yes","footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-379","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-notes"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/hpmor.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/379","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/hpmor.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/hpmor.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hpmor.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hpmor.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=379"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/hpmor.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/379\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/hp